title: Ebro In The Morning - WWE Champion Big E + Legendary Rapper AZ
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
WWE World Champion Big E sits down with Ebro in the Morning to discuss his feelings after winning the title, words that Vince McMahon said to him following that night, his thoughts on Goldberg, as well as his football career and life before he got into the sports entertainment business. 

Legendary MC AZ sits down with Ebro in the Morning to go down memory lane, talk about inspiration from Nas and Jay-Z, working with Lil Wayne, T-Pain, Rick Ross & Conway, and his new project 'Do Or Die 2'. 

Subscribe to Ebro In The Morning !
